%% Diagram: OOP-R IPC flow between renderer and Viz process
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as Renderer<br/>main thread
    participant CC as Renderer<br/>cc compositor
    participant Worker as Renderer<br/>raster worker
    participant Viz as Viz / GPU process<br/>(Skia + driver)

    Main->>CC: commit PaintRecord
    CC->>Worker: schedule tile (NOW)
    Worker->>Worker: serialize Skia ops<br/>to command buffer
    Worker->>Viz: IPC: raster cmds + sync token
    Viz->>Viz: Skia (Ganesh / Graphite)<br/>replays via GL / Vulkan / Metal / D3D12
    Viz-->>Worker: sync token released<br/>texture under mailbox
    CC->>Viz: CompositorFrame<br/>referencing mailbox
    Viz->>Viz: present frame at VBlank
